In its 35th season, the dinnertime show is suddenly appointment television as Holzhauer has shattered the idea of a typical “Jeopardy!” strategy.
“That’s honestly one of the smartest things James is doing, going for the high dollar values early,” Jennings told Wired.
It’s really, really smart.
